            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1318.-step-2-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1318.-step-2-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1318.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, zest your<strong> lemon[s]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>(try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter!)</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1318.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1318.-step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1318.-step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1318.-step-3-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1318.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>lemon zest</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>,<strong> lamb mince</strong>, <strong>panko breadcrumbs</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Mix thoroughly until fully combined (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Divide the <strong>mixture</strong> and roll them into 6 meatballs per person</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
