      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once cooked, remove the <strong>lemony lamb</strong> <strong>meatballs</strong> from the oven and add them to the bowl of <strong>harissa dressing</strong></p><p>Gently mix the <strong>meatballs</strong> into the <strong>dressing</strong> until fully coated – these are your <strong>dressed lamb meatballs</strong></p><p>Rinse the <strong>salted cucumber</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong> and shake off any excess liquid</p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into 1 wedge per person</p>",
      "order": 7,
