    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>bulgur wheat </strong>with your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> to the side (spread the yoghurt out with the back of a spoon)</p><p>Top with the <strong>salted cucumber </strong>and <strong>dressed lamb meatballs</strong></p><p>Drizzle over any <strong>remaining dressing</strong>, garnish with the <strong>chopped herbs</strong> and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
